<SECOND>AM-Soviet-Ship Fire,0221</SECOND>
<HEAD>Soviet Passenger Ship Catches Fire; All Aboard Reported Safe</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MOSCOW (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
