<SECOND>AM-Lebanon,0336</SECOND>
<HEAD>Amal Beats Up Hijacker Hamadi's Brother</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By FAROUK NASSAR</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
